{"tid":2322450,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TMA／韓當日確診950人＋MAMA被罵爆！　這次演員頒獎人也得戴口罩","createTime":"2020-12-12T10:33:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T11:53:55.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3a7908690c0ad45549a58c1d0136b18bee6a9eee","tid":2322450,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T10:33:15.000Z","msg":"南韓音樂盛典MAMA（Mnet Asian Music Awards）日前頒獎典禮結束後，被網友指出主辦單位對待演員和偶像歌手有差別待遇，包括偶像領獎時要戴口罩，頒獎的演員卻不需要。而隨著12日南韓當日確診人數飆破950人，當天舉辦的「The Fact Music Awards」（TMA），終於連頒獎的演員也戴上口罩了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5330/d5330661.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5330%2Fd5330661.jpg&h=c643d8c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲TMA頒獎人也要戴上口罩，圖為演員朴海鎮。（圖／翻攝自播出畫面）<br />\n<br />\n南韓音樂盛典「The Fact Music Awards」（TMA）12日晚間7點在首爾舉行，因應疫情，紅毯採取事先錄製的方式播出。包括防彈少年團（BTS）、SUPER JUNIOR、TWICE、NU&rsquo;EST、GOT7、SEVENTEEN、MAMAMOO、姜丹尼爾、Jessi、IZ*ONE、(G)I-DLE等20組藝人現身。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5330/d5330665.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5330%2Fd5330665.jpg&h=4209d63a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲防彈少年團領獎時戴口罩，並自備麥克風致詞。（圖／翻攝自播出畫面）<br />\n<br />\n典禮第一位頒獎人是演員朴海鎮，他現身為頒發「年度藝人」獎和人氣獎，上台時就戴好的口罩。或許因先前MAMA引起的「演員、偶像差別待遇」爭議，也可能是南韓確診人數不斷創新高，這回終於台上所有人都做好了防護。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5330/d5330667.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5330%2Fd5330667.jpg&h=002cd147&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ITZY擔任TMA頒獎人時戴上口罩。（圖／翻攝自播出畫面）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一個有趣的亮點是，當朴海鎮頒獎時，打開信封後說：「有兩個得獎者，MAMAMOO和華莎！」有趣的形成一組團體上台，但包括兩個得獎者的情況。Super Junior獲獎時，則因為瀏海和口罩幾乎連在一起，被主持人虧說：「希澈看得到路嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5330/d5330662.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5330%2Fd5330662.jpg&h=48ccdf23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲MAMAMOO領獎。（圖／翻攝自播出畫面）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5330/d5330690.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5330%2Fd5330690.jpg&h=d550178f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Super Junior領獎，希澈（右一）被虧「看得到嗎？」（圖／翻攝自播出畫面）"},{"pid":"8118dc4e04f76bd84f6080a98e2cf601d5a5749a","tid":2322450,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T11:51:25.000Z","msg":"希澈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c974598a79b6da27c924e1546d52fdc544c85d6","tid":2322450,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8118dc4e04f76bd84f6080a98e2cf601d5a5749a","tid":2322450,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T11:51:25.000Z","msg":"希澈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T11:53:55.000Z","msg":"Dead please<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}